doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="IE=edge")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="public/styles/global.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="public/styles/navbar.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="public/styles/homepage.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="public/styles/footer.css")

  body
    include ../navbar.pug
    main.container-fluid.py-5.px-0
        #carouselExampleCaptions.carousel.slide.px-5(data-bs-ride="carousel")
            .carousel-indicators.bg-dark.mx-5.mb-0.bg-opacity-80
                button(type="button", data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions", data-bs-slide-to="0", class="active", aria-current="true", aria-label="Slide 1")
                button(type="button", data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions", data-bs-slide-to="1", aria-label="Slide 2")
                button(type="button", data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions", data-bs-slide-to="2", aria-label="Slide 3")

            .carousel-inner
                .carousel-item.active
                    img.carousel-img.d-block.w-100.rounded-1(height="600", src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2015/03/11/05/05/dry-fish-668199_960_720.jpg", alt="...")
                    .carousel-caption.d-none.d-md-block.bg-dark.w-100.start-0.end-0.bg-opacity-50
                        h5 First slide label
                        p Some representative placeholder content for the first slide.

                .carousel-item
                    img.carousel-img.d-block.w-100.rounded-1(height="600", src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2019/03/05/12/26/fish-4036085_960_720.jpg", alt="...")
                    .carousel-caption.d-none.d-md-block.bg-dark.w-100.start-0.end-0.bg-opacity-50
                        h5 Second slide label
                        p Some representative placeholder content for the second slide.

                .carousel-item
                    img.carousel-img.d-block.w-100.rounded-1(height="600", src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2014/01/04/10/46/fishing-boats-238404_960_720.jpg", alt="...")
                    .carousel-caption.d-none.d-md-block.bg-dark.w-100.start-0.end-0.bg-opacity-50
                        h5 Third slide label
                        p Some representative placeholder content for the third slide.

            button.carousel-control-prev(type="button", data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions", data-bs-slide="prev")
                span.carousel-control-prev-icon(aria-hidden="true")
                span.visually-hidden Previous

            button.carousel-control-next(type="button", data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions", data-bs-slide="next")
                span.carousel-control-next-icon(aria-hidden="true")
                span.visually-hidden Next

        hr.border.border-1.border-dark.my-5.mx-5

        .container-fluid.background-biru-muda-50.py-5.px-5
            .card.mb-3.border-0(style="max-width: 100%;")
                .row.g-0
                    .col-md-4.background-biru-muda-50
                        img.img-fluid.rounded-start(src="https://imageplaceholder.net/600", alt="img")
                    .col-md-8.background-biru-muda-50
                        #card-body.card-body.pe-0.py-0.h-100.d-flex.flex-column.justify-content-between
                            h2.card-title.kuning.fw-bold.text-wrap(style="width: 60%") Kelezatan Laut, Dalam Satu Klik
                            p.card-text.text-wrap.lh-md.pt-3.pb-4.fs-5(style="width:80%") Belanja hasil laut segar dan olahan dengan mudah dan cepat. Kami hadirkan pilihan terbaik, dari ikan, udang, cumi, hingga produk olahan siap masak. Tidak perlu lagi repot ke pasar tradisional, cukup pesan dari kenyamanan rumah Anda. Kami bekerja sama dengan nelayan dan pemasok terpercaya untuk memastikan kesegaran dan kualitas produk terjaga.
                            a.card-text.text-decoration-none.text-dark.fw-bold.background-kuning.px-3.py-2.rounded-1(href="#", style="width: fit-content;") Explore Now

        .container-fluid.my-5.px-5
            .border.py-4
                h3.text-center.pb-0.fw-bold Rekomendasi Produk
                .py-4.d-flex.flex-wrap.justify-content-center
                    each val in [1, 2, 3]
                        .card.mx-4.my-1(style="width: 20rem;")
                            img.card-img-top(src="https://imageplaceholder.net/400x300", alt="...")
                            .card-body
                                h5.card-title Nama Produk
                                p.card-text Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the bulk of the card's content.
                                p.biru-laut
                                    svg(xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg", x="0px", y="0px", width="20", height="20", viewBox="0,0,256,256")
                                        g(fill="#006094", fill-rule="nonzero", stroke="none", stroke-width="1", stroke-linecap="butt", stroke-linejoin="miter", stroke-miterlimit="10", stroke-dasharray="", stroke-dashoffset="0", font-family="none", font-weight="none", font-size="none", text-anchor="none", style="mix-blend-mode: normal")
